title: Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2668/89 of 30 August 1989 amending Annexes III and IV bis to Council Regulation (EEC) No 4136/86 with regard to certain textile products originating in Pakistan (category 4)
header:
COMMISSION  REGULATION (EEC) No 2668/89
of 30 August 1989
amending Annexes III and IV bis to Council Regulation (EEC) No 4136/86 with regard to certain textile products originating in Pakistan (category 4)
THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
main_body: Annexes III and IV bis to Regulation (EEC) No 4136/86 are hereby amended for Pakistan in accordance with the Annex hereto.

This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities.
It shall apply with effect from 1 January 1989.
This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.
attachments:
Done at Brussels, 30 August 1989.
For the Commission
Karel VAN MIERT
Member of the Commission
(1) OJ No L 387, 31. 12. 1986, p. 42.
(2) OJ No L 79, 22. 3. 1989, p. 6.
